# Code Owners
# This file defines who should review specific parts of the codebase
# Learn more: https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositorys-settings-and-features/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners

# Global owners - will be requested for review on all PRs
* @devops-team @senior-developers

# GitHub Actions and CI/CD workflows
/.github/ @devops-team @platform-team

# Source code - requires developer review
/src/ @senior-developers @backend-team

# Tests - QA team should review test changes  
/tests/ @qa-team @backend-team

# Configuration files - DevOps and senior developers
*.json @devops-team @senior-developers
*.js @senior-developers
*.yml @devops-team
*.yaml @devops-team

# Documentation - Technical writers and team leads
/docs/ @technical-writers @team-leads
README.md @technical-writers @team-leads
CONTRIBUTING.md @team-leads

# Security and compliance
.eslintrc.js @security-team @senior-developers
jest.config.js @qa-team @senior-developers
package.json @devops-team @senior-developers

# Infrastructure and deployment scripts
/scripts/ @devops-team @platform-team